    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, always kept in the garage, and I\u2019ve stayed on top of every single maintenance check. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is definitely the one. You\u2019ve gotta see it to believe how clean it is! Feel free to reach out if you want to take a look.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
