      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is a museum-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera (996.2). This example features the 3.6L flat-six powerplant equipped with VarioCam Plus, delivering a linear power band and an unmistakable boxer note. Mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, the mechanical engagement is peerless. The chassis remains taut, retaining its factory-spec dampening and lateral stiffness. Recent borescope inspection confirms zero scoring, and the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed with a dual-row ceramic solution. The exterior retains its original deep-luster clear coat over a perfectly preserved body, while the undercarriage remains free of any electrolytic corrosion or fluid seepage. A true driver\u2019s specimen in collector-grade state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
