    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable specimen that defines the standard for 'mint' condition. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, seeing only fair-weather use. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic gloss, free of any stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, and has been treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating for lasting protection. Every body panel is original with perfect factory gaps. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains soft and matte with absolutely no bolster wear or creasing, and the high-gloss trim is free of micro-scratches. All electronic systems, including the advanced driver assistance suite and infotainment, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach. It features a comprehensive service portfolio with every maintenance interval performed ahead of schedule at an authorized dealership. The engine bay is concours-level clean, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road debris or oxidation. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and performs exactly as it did on the showroom floor.",
      "price": 43500.0,
