      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it in the garage, and never missed a service. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s practically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 44900.0,
