    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an exceptional E46 M3, a masterclass in atmospheric induction and chassis balance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been meticulously shimmed for peak volumetric efficiency. This specimen is mechanically flawless, having undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral G-loads. The ZF 6-speed manual gearbox provides tactile engagement, feeding power through a variable M differential lock. The exterior remains in showroom condition with original paint depth and no panel gap deviations, while the interior retains its factory matte finish on all touchpoints. This is a collector-grade example with zero deferred maintenance, ready for the most discerning enthusiast.",
